add

public boolean add(byte[] tag,
                   byte[] length,
                   byte[] value)
Tries to identify the given data by tag/file id and to parse the given data (value). If successful the data is added internally to the CardData for XML dump.

Parameters:
tag - byte array with tag value & data/signature indicator (2 + 1 bytes)
length - byte array that contains the length of the value (2 bytes)
value - byte array with data
Returns:
true if parsing of the given byte array was successful
